snippet.textDisplay:
Real mean of You think you know me?
Well, Edge is one of those superstars that you won't appreciate as a kid but will love when you're old enough. I really despised him when I was a kid. Because he was nasty and he was playing as the bad boy or opposition. We were meant to boo him.
But now I can see clearly that Edge is and always was a Badass. It's funny like how his theme song relates with my view of him. But the reality is that watching his comeback sure brings back memories.
The fact that he's back after 9 years is heartwarming.
Last time I was booing him but now I'm *cheering him*. Life is funny sometimes.
snippet.textOriginal:
Real mean of *You think you know me?*
Well, Edge is one of those superstars that you won't appreciate as a kid but will love when you're old enough. I really despised him when I was a kid. Because he was nasty and he was playing as the bad boy or opposition. We were meant to boo him.
 *But now I can see clearly* that Edge is and always was a Badass. It's funny like how his theme song relates with my view of him. But the reality is that watching his comeback sure brings back memories.
The fact that he's back after 9 years is heartwarming.
*Last time I was booing him* but now I'm *cheering him*. Life is funny sometimes.
